snippet.title: Theropods: A Pixelated Prehistoric Adventure
snippet.description:
Theropods is a point-and-click adventure game that blends puzzles with a cinematic story, colorful characters, and a retro aesthetic. 

Travel back in time to the era when ancient beasts ruled the Earth and adventure games were in the spotlight. Lose yourself in a vast, prehistoric world full of dinosaurs, lovingly crafted PIXEL by PIXEL.

Links: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1091870/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=trailer&utm_campaign=organic
